{"type": "article", "id": 24827, "title": "彩色餐具", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-01T06:54:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115112jEb6zclXknYCQmZA.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">法国厨具品牌 Le Creuset 的特色就是彩色的铁锅，他们和便利店 7-Eleven 一起合作推出了一套彩色的餐具。手柄的颜色可以对应到锅的颜色，另一头用上了迷你版的锅或者南瓜的形状，除了方便旅行携带还有收藏的意义。这是一套女生会喜欢的餐具，目前还没有上市。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115109jxto8NFfyqISiwap.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115110djEXrq3Hy0kwuOzQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115110rs5EezoiYwhvSNQb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115111DGlAtnFRrchVWjMg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115111zrW0USMEkgo4tXO7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}